Program: Omnibus
Title: The Korubo
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376lfl
Last Broadcast Date: 03 February 1997
A journey in search of the Korubo tribe, one of the last remaining Indian tribes, who live deep in the Amazon basin on the frontier with Peru. Sidney Possuelo leads an expedition to find the indigenious people and offer protection for their way of life.